WEBVTT

1
00:00:03.120 --> 00:00:17.970
Patrick Garvin: A web content accessibility guidelines are a collection of guidelines based on four principles. Those principles are what are called the poor principles.

2
00:00:19.109 --> 00:00:24.000
Patrick Garvin: Perceivable, operable, understandable and robust.

3
00:00:25.740 --> 00:00:35.640
Patrick Garvin: These principles are the basis of web content accessibility efforts across the world.

4
00:00:39.870 --> 00:00:48.360
Patrick Garvin: The web content accessibility guidelines are often referred to as wcag or WCAG.

5
00:00:50.250 --> 00:00:57.060
Patrick Garvin: They have evolved over the last 23 years.

6
00:00:58.380 --> 00:01:03.360
Patrick Garvin: And that are going to continue to evolve and grow.
